message.entry: The specified frequency resolution value is too large. The FrequencyResolution property must be < {0} {1}.
The specified frequency resolution is not attainable with the input data length. The FrequencyResolution property must be > {0} {1}.
The specified measurement bands are outside the Nyquist interval of [-SampleRate/2 SampleRate/2] when NormalizedFrequency is false, or [-1 1] when NormalizedFrequency is true.
